Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBArchive

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBArchive
public class JDBArchive
extends java.lang.Object
JDBArchive class is used to insert/update/delete the SYS_ARCHIVE table. The SYS_ARCHIVE table is a user definable auto archiving system. In essence a SQL delete statement with date parameter can be inserted into this table. At a predetermined interval the Archiving Thread executes each statement in this table to remove old/unneeded records from tables.

See Also:
JInternalFrameArchiveAdmin, JDialogArchiveProperties
